Pete Evans has been dropped as the celebrity ambassador for salad chain 'Sumo Salad' The food chain maintains that the decision was not related to his recent paleo controversies . 
  Evans has announced that his baby cookbook 'Bubba Yum Yum: The Paleo Way' is set to be self-published this month . 
  The cookbook was delayed due to fatal health concerns . 
  Evans was dropped as a celebrity ambassador by the salad chain . 
  Sumo Salad maintains that they did not renew his two-year contract . 
 